       S9000-FINAL-RTN.
      *@5.1 폼ID SET
      *@처리내용:화면폼ID SET
           #BOFMID 'V1KJL11085000'

           #OKEXIT  CO-STAT-OK .
       S9000-FINAL-EXT.
